'''Herron Berrian''' (born 31 December 1994, [[Liberia]]) is a [[Liberia]]n football player, who plays as an [[Attacking Midfielder]] for  [[Panserraikos 1964 F.C.|Panserraikos]].<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://int.soccerway.com/players/berrian-herron/263376/|title=Liberia - H. Berrian - Profile with news, career statistics and history - Soccerway|website=int.soccerway.com|language=en|access-date=2018-05-03}}</ref>

